### Steps to change design
When you have been asked to change the design on components you must follow these steps to complete the task:
- Use global MUI styles to redesign components.
- Update styles of Material UI components for components in src/common/components and src/modules directories.
- Update icon for the website in public/icon.svg, use landing icon landing/public/icon.svg
- Update site name in index.html, use project_name from landing/generator/placeholders.txt
- You must update site name in src/modules/login/Login.tsx component, use project_name from landing/generator/placeholders.txt

- If you were not provided with images/svg icons for website content you must generate svg icons it on your own.